#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To help you get started, &step; integrates a series of tutorials which "
"easily teach you how to build an experiment. Please see step by step to "
"start with the first tutorial."
msgstr ""
"Alustamise hõlbustamiseks pakub &step; mitut õppematerjali, mis näitavad, "
"kuidas katse üles ehitada. Palun uuri kõike lähemalt alates esimesest "
"õppematerjalist."

